### Phase 4: Supabase Service Layer

Create service modules that encapsulate all database operations. Each service provides CRUD functions and maintains the same contract expected by the UI components.

#### [NEW] [apartments.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/services/apartments.service.ts)
**Functions:**
- `getApartments()` - Fetch all apartments with bag info (joins bags table)
- `getApartment(id)` - Fetch single apartment
- `createApartment(data, bagItems)` - Create apartment (bag auto-created by trigger)
- [updateApartment(id, data)](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/hooks/useAppState.tsx#74-79) - Update apartment details
- [deleteApartment(id)](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/hooks/useAppState.tsx#79-87) - Delete apartment (cascades to bag and missions)
- `updateICalLink(id, link)` - Update iCal sync URL

#### [NEW] [bags.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/services/bags.service.ts)
**Functions:**
- `getBags()` - Fetch all bags with apartment and item details
- `getBag(id)` - Fetch single bag with items
- [updateBagStatus(id, status)](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/hooks/useAppState.tsx#110-122) - Update bag status
- [updateBagItems(id, items)](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/hooks/useAppState.tsx#122-142) - Update bag contents (replaces all items)
- `checkBagStockAvailability(id)` - Check if stock is sufficient

#### [NEW] [missions.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/services/missions.service.ts)
**Functions:**
- `getMissions(filters?)` - Fetch missions with optional date/status/agent filters
- `getMission(id)` - Fetch single mission with full details
- `createMission(data)` - Create new mission
- [updateMissionStatus(id, status)](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/hooks/useAppState.tsx#87-110) - Update mission status (triggers bag status sync)
- [assignAgent(id, agentId)](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/hooks/useAppState.tsx#165-177) - Assign agent to mission
- `deleteMission(id)` - Delete mission

#### [NEW] [stock.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/services/stock.service.ts)
**Functions:**
- `getStockItems()` - Fetch all stock items
- `getStockItem(id)` - Fetch single stock item
- `createStockItem(data)` - Create new stock item
- [updateStockQuantity(id, quantity)](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/hooks/useAppState.tsx#142-154) - Update stock quantity (triggers bag status updates)
- `deleteStockItem(id)` - Delete stock item

#### [NEW] [reservations.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/services/reservations.service.ts)
**Functions:**
- `getReservations(apartmentId?)` - Fetch reservations
- `syncICalFeed(apartmentId)` - Fetch and parse iCal, create/update reservations
- `createReservation(data)` - Manually create reservation
- `deleteReservation(id)` - Delete reservation

#### [NEW] [users.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/services/users.service.ts)
**Functions:**
- `getUsers()` - Fetch all users
- `getUser(id)` - Fetch single user
- `getCurrentUserProfile()` - Get current user's profile from users table
- `createUserProfile(authId, data)` - Create user profile linked to auth

