### Phase 5: State Management Refactor

#### [MODIFY] [useAppState.tsx](file:///c:/Users/dry-_/OneDrive/Bureau/Apios/conciergerie/src/hooks/useAppState.tsx)
**Changes:**
- Replace `useState` with `useEffect` to fetch data on mount
- Replace mock data imports with service function calls
- Implement loading and error states
- Keep optimistic updates for better UX
- Add real-time subscriptions (optional)

**Strategy:**
- Maintain the same context API so components don't need changes
- Load all data on mount (apartments, bags, missions, stock)
- User mutations call Supabase services and update local state
- Consider implementing real-time subscriptions for collaborative features

